# 6. あなた達のためのショー

Emu: Hehe. First here again!
Emu: But...
Emu: Hmm... My eyes are still all red... Even after putting in those eye drops...
Emu: (What do I do? If the others see me like this, they're gonna start wondering if I'm okay...)
???: <Emmuuu!>
Emu: Wah! Wh-Who was that?
Emu: Oh! Hi, MEIKO!
MEIKO: <Sorry, I didn't mean to startle you! Huh...? Emu, your eyes...>
Emu: What...?! N-No, I'm fine! I just... I stayed up all night playing video games!
MEIKO: <You did...?>
Emu: A-Anyway, MEIKO, is something the matter?
MEIKO: <Ah, right! There's something I need to tell all of you...>
Emu: Hmm... The others should be here soon... But do you want me to relay your message to them?
MEIKO: <You'd do that? Then, if you don't mind...>
MEIKO: <The thing is...>
MEIKO: <Before you all start practicing, we'd like you to come see our show!>
Emu: Huh?
