MEIKO: <But you've all been looking a little down!>
MEIKO: <What shows need are... Passion! Energy! And above all else, smiles!>
MEIKO: <Which is why we decided to put on a special show for you all that's guaranteed to turn those frowns upside down!!!>
Emu: A special show?
MEIKO: <Yes, we'd very much like for you all to see it. So, how about it?!>
Emu: Yeah! We'll for sure come see it! Thanks, MEIKO!
Emu: Then, once the others get here, we'll all go over together... Oh, wait...
MEIKO: <Hm? Is something wrong?>
Emu: Um... You know how my eyes are still a little red? You were worried when you first saw me, MEIKO, so I was wondering if I could do something about it before the others get here...
MEIKO: <Then, I have the perfect solution!>
MEIKO: <Come with me to SEKAI right now, Emu! I'll invite the others myself! And while I'm doing that...>
Tsukasa: Okay, MEIKO asked us to come see this show of theirs, and we're here...
Tsukasa: Where's Emu?
